<h1> <center>Welcome to the International Students Message Board </h1></center>
</br>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">

		<p> This forum will make it easier for members to communicate and keep in touch. Feel free to ask questions, offer comments, and please let us know how we can improve the site. We value all user feedback as it makes the experience better for everyone. Enjoy! </p>
		<h2> Latest Messages </h2>

		<% if user_signed_in? %>
			<h4><%= link_to "New Message", new_message_path, class: "navbar-right navbar-text navbar-link" %></h4>
		<% end %>

		<!-- Not doing it in the correct place -->
		<% @messages.each do |message| %>
			<h2><%= message.title %></h2>
			<%= link_to "View Message", message_path(message), class: "btn btn-success", :style => 'color:#FFFFFF;'%>
		<% end %>

</div>
</div>
